This database currently has approximately 337,700 records consisting of residential and business telephone numbers listed for public access. The geographical areas covered by this set of data include all postal zip codes from 32000-32099 and 32601-32697.
You may make broad searches with general search criteria such as Find All Account Names in Zip Code"32601"which will return 18,303 businesses and residential telephone account names. You may narrow the search by using multiple search criteria which will reveal a smaller"Found Set"of records.
Be sure to clear old search definitions before beginning a new search.
